originalText.text:
Everytime the exterminator comes to my apartment and sprays for roaches the situation gets worse like he's feeding them steroids I have never had issue's with roaches before I started letting the exterminator into my apartment I will never allow him back in.

Mice in my apartment are eating the pinkish cake pouches the exterminator is leaving through out my apartment and I haven't seen a dead mouse yet is it possible that he's feeding them steroids as well the situation is getting worse.

I believe if any extermination company could solve a pest problem they would be out of a job so this is why I believe that the service provided by the exterminator is bogus and a waste of time and money the extermination business is a scam and a Fraud especially (Castro extermination) we have 48 apartments here in this building complex and after the tenants meetings we have held we have come to the conclusion that ( Castro extermination ) has to be replaced with a more effective method or company also we are already hiring a handyman to fill in all the cracks and crevasse through out the 48 apartments we are having issue's with this Technic should have been done by Castro extermination person who services this building.
